{"tid":1698831,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"各屯元天街坊： 唔理你仲有無坐黨鐵，唔該認住呢個南亞仔敗類。","createTime":"2019-11-07T19:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T03:39:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"26284b9831ecc37796862f97f53c354517768ea4","tid":1698831,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:04:27.000Z","msg":"#手動轉<br />\n<br />\n各屯元天街坊：<br />\n唔理你仲有無坐黨鐵，唔該認住呢個南亞仔敗類。<br />\n佢每日都喺唔同嘅西鐵站呃人買單程票，過海，一張30蚊。<br />\n多謝完你轉頭就去客務中心要求退票。<br />\n佢一次30蚊，佢每日嘅工作就係做呢樣嘢，好好賺。<br />\n<br />\n專呃啲年青人，會用英文講佢有急事要去中環，有時甚至會呃多張小童飛（$15）！<br />\n<br />\n認住佢，南亞人之恥！<br />\n屯元天果幾個站都係佢活動範圍！<br />\n有錢，買多張飯卷比小朋友好過！<br />\n<br />\n如果佢真係咁有需要，大家可以叫佢去客務中心，黨鐵可以賖票比佢，要留佢身份証/護照資料同地址電話！<br />\n唔好再比佢呃錢！"},{"pid":"a537a307cacc99dace9e72ed6459dca2b339e669","tid":1698831,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:04:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/119187851842460/permalink/816839865410585?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F119187851842460%2Fpermalink%2F816839865410585%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=d864d563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/119187851842460/permalink/816839865410585?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"a8219f330ea1e5d6072c40bab0eebe276c1476ee","tid":1698831,"uid":109115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d57636a2786183a56dc369f33ba953c6fdafd7f","tid":1698831,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def37a610f6d61586ee09dcd1df0d9e3b21a89b7","tid":1698831,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:17:40.000Z","msg":"唔好亂做好人啦<br />\n好多呃人"},{"pid":"4f74e34e83d1da4